lead_paragraph: Jack Nicklaus says he thinks Tiger Woods will win again. After seeing him a few weeks ago, Nicklaus is surprised Woods isn't playing the Masters this week.

headline.print_headline: Nicklaus: Tiger Isn't Done Just Yet
headline.main: Nicklaus: Tiger Isn't Done Just Yet
